  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2913770/extras/ec8be0d43a28f7709ffb6ab94d82c163.avif?t=1714145038\" width=544 height=86 /></span><br><strong>A first-person 3D psychological horror. Phantasm is a puzzle game</strong>, where you must apply logical and reasoning skills to go further. There are many locks, keys, hints, 10+ rooms with puzzles, and everything you expect from a stunning horror game.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2913770/extras/e50bbe1e0656bbf91ed34815f75b99c1.avif?t=1714145038\" width=544 height=174 /></span><br>You receive a call asking you to go through a series of “simple” tests to earn $100 billion and one cherished wish. However, ordinary tasks gradually turn into sheer horror. How will this all end? Are you ready to take on the challenge and find out the truth?",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2913770/extras/ec8be0d43a28f7709ffb6ab94d82c163.avif?t=1714145038\" width=544 height=86 /></span><br><strong>A first-person 3D psychological horror. Phantasm is a puzzle game</strong>, where you must apply logical and reasoning skills to go further. There are many locks, keys, hints, 10+ rooms with puzzles, and everything you expect from a stunning horror game.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2913770/extras/e50bbe1e0656bbf91ed34815f75b99c1.avif?t=1714145038\" width=544 height=174 /></span><br>You receive a call asking you to go through a series of “simple” tests to earn $100 billion and one cherished wish. However, ordinary tasks gradually turn into sheer horror. How will this all end? Are you ready to take on the challenge and find out the truth?",
